- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep neural networks and model compression, which are both relevant to AI research. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions evaluating the method on a wide range of benchmarks, which could include computer vision tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with neural networks and their compression.
